     <h1 class="title2">
      Welcome
     </h1>
     <div style="width:180px; height: 300px; float: right; margin-left: 10px;">
      <p>
       <a href="http://profiles.uthscsa.edu/?pid=profile&amp;id=0V71EUDYE">
